snippet.title: Whoopi Goldberg ‘erupts’ after Justice says a fetus ‘has an interest in having a life’
snippet.description:
Sky News host Cory Bernardi says actress Whoopi Goldberg “erupted on television” after Supreme Court Justice Samuel Alito said a fetus “has an interest in having a life”. 

Ms Goldberg slammed the comments Justice Alito made during a debate about a Mississippi abortion ban and said men don’t have a right to talk about what a fetus wants because they cannot carry one. 

“Here’s the problem with what Whoopi said. She’s going to get cancelled because the woke left says that men can have babies, they can carry fetuses, they can chest feed,” Mr Bernardi said.
